  lines:
  - english: Fine wares!
    swedish: Fina varor
  - english: Freshly baked bread here!
    swedish: Nybakat brod har
  - english: Feel your stomach rumbling?
    swedish: Kanner du kurret i magen
  - english: Stew or waybread? I have them both!
    swedish: Gryta eller vagbrod jag har dem bagge
  - english: Good food for good prices!
    swedish: Bra mat for bra priser
